Package: siteBayes
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Methods for Site-Specific Treatment Effect Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "JoonHo", "Lee",
      email = "jlee296@ua.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: siteBayes provides Bayesian methods for estimating and analyzing 
    site-specific treatment effects in multisite trials. The package includes 
    flexible semiparametric modeling and alternative posterior summary methods 
    to improve the estimation and ranking of treatment effects across sites.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
